I'm gonna see things.

1536
01:28:53.091 --> 01:28:53.730
I'm gonna see things.

1537
01:28:53.790 --> 01:28:54.830
Breathe through your nose.

1538
01:28:54.870 --> 01:28:55.910
Breathe through your nose.

1539
